text: Thörnqvist or Thornqvist is a Swedish surname that may refer to: *Anna Thörnqvist (born 1995), a Swedish footballer *Jan Thörnqvist (born 1959), a Swedish Navy vice admiral *Owe Thörnqvist (born 1929), a Swedish singer- songwriter and revue artist *Roland Thornqvist (born 1970), an American college tennis coach and college tennis player Category:Swedish-language surnames
